text: Isa Pang Bahaghari (English: "Another Rainbow") is a 2020 film starring Nora Aunor. It is directed by Joel Lamangan. https://push.abs- cbn.com/2019/7/23/fresh-scoops/nora-aunor-tirso-cruz-iii-at-boyet-de-leon- reuni-212290 https://www.pep.ph/pepalerts/142146/christopher-nora-tirso- magkakaroon-ng-reunion-movie-a4118-20190331 It is one of the official entries for the 2020 Metro Manila Summer Film Festival. The official trailer was launched on October 8, 2019 at the CineBravo Facebook page. ==Cast== *Nora Aunor *Phillip Salvador *Michael de Mesa *Zanjoe Marudo *Joseph Marco *Sanya Lopez *Maris Racal *Albie Casiño *Migs Almendras Nora Aunor ==References== Category:2020 films Category:Philippine films Category:Films not released in theaters due to the COVID-19 pandemic
